        ---------
        
        Michael Greenacre, JÃ¶rg Blasius (2006). `Multiple Correspondence Analysis and Related Methods <http://www.crcpress.com/product/isbn/9781584886280>`_, CRC Press. ISBN 1584886285.
        
        
        
